headline: 5 Top-Ranked Retail Apparel and Shoe Stocks for a Stable Portfolio
summary: DECK, ONON, TPR, AEO and FIGS are five top-ranked apparel and shoe stocks poised for stability in 2026 as steady demand and brand strength drive growth.
